{"type": "article", "id": 27295, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-25T06:31:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28094, "name": "Rule/One"}, {"id": 28095, "name": "HMM"}, {"id": 28096, "name": "XOCO"}, {"id": 28097, "name": "Michiel Cornelissen Ontwerp"}, {"id": 28098, "name": "Taga"}, {"id": 28099, "name": "Eclipse Sconce"}, {"id": 28100, "name": "DrinkMate"}, {"id": 28101, "name": "Edge Tech Labs"}, {"id": 28102, "name": "El Golfo de México"}, {"id": 28103, "name": "Colateral Advanced Marketing"}, {"id": 28104, "name": "Roll & Hill"}, {"id": 28105, "name": "Philippe Malouin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132408PlE2qZebNgGwfmKn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Rule/One by HMM</h2>\n<p>来自台湾的 <a href=\"http://hmmproject.com/\">HMM</a> 设计团队一直专注于改造我们习以为常的日常用品，最近他们推出了一款便携的尺笔合一的文具。Rule/One 的尺和笔之间通过磁贴吸附在一起，侧面看就好像滴液一样，可以当作书签或镇纸使用。如果你的办公已经完全去纸化，它配备的电容笔头能让你在各类触屏设备上进行工作。这是它的<a href=\"http://hmmproject.com/products/rule-one\">购买链接</a>，售价 60 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160200SW3xias2HfhtUYL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7552381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021602000C96VxINaMwhfEX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160211NX849fJDBPeHSZp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160212D9h3jpOZrHqLVblJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160212tNuQgarnyHf1Mhiw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160213jmb60AvwxaoFeBX9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>XOCO 3D printer by Michiel Cornelissen Ontwerp</h2>\n<p>3D 打印技术很常见，但你见过用它做食物的吗？荷兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.michielcornelissen.com/\">Michiel Cornelissen Ontwerp</a> 最近就推出了一款比较特殊的 3D 打印机，使用巧克力作为“墨水”，帮助人们在家轻松实现 DIY 巧克力的梦想。这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.michielcornelissen.com/portfolio_page/xoco-chocolate-printer/\">XOCO</a> 的打印机采用了透明的玻璃罩，给人一种童话里出现的小工坊的感觉。用户通过配套的手机应用自定义巧克力的形状后就很直观地看到制作的全过程，底部的 LED 光环还可以显示过程的进度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021602145ozIcFTOdAYanSXN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160215brzWsP8e3vXAIRdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160215ZYKuGA1rbTm6gtkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160216mUzBLWfTH6Z2sv8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Taga 2.0 by Taga USA Inc.</h2>\n<p>想骑着自行车和孩子一起出行？你可能需要这辆家用自行车 Taga。它的设计灵感来自荷兰的货载自行车，它们通常在前面放置了一个可以盛放货物的木箱——而 Taga 搭载的是可以折叠并且自由组合的箱体，配套的组件有婴儿椅、扶手、遮阳篷甚至水枪，可以满足家庭出行的各种需要。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/taga2/taga-20-the-ultimate-most-affordable-family-bike\">链接</a>参与它的众筹，如果你不清楚该购买哪些配套组件，专用的<a href=\"https://tross.typeform.com/to/gihTEP\">导购页面</a>可以帮你完成个性化的定制。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160216UnjWrFmSB4lCsfy7.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160218H3h4m7DbMenGrtCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93083573\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160219fNR9jeS7J3bVYzsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91285081\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160220JGOfTEe9ohHw8Xgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92690058\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Eclipse Sconce by Philippe Malouin</h2>\n<p>觉得造型单纯模仿星体太乏味？不妨来看看这个能让你在家“观测”到天文现象的灯具吧。加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://philippemalouin.com/\">Philippe Malouin</a> 最近为 <a href=\"http://www.rollandhill.com/\">Roll &amp; Hill</a> 设计了一款名为 Eclipse Sconce 的壁灯，通过简洁设计还原了神奇的日食景象。包裹在灯外部的是一个光滑的半球体灯罩，通过推拉下端的短杆就能调整灯罩与墙之间的距离，灯光效果也会随之变化。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.rollandhill.com/collections/philippe-malouin/products/eclipse-sconce\">购买链接</a>，售价为 950 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216022023TqNp5xOUjSdXIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160221SCH6jDgMp271fEot.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160221kf9X7jZo436EVzdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160222ia54gHKtwRGbP9Iu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>DrinkMate by Edge Tech Labs</h2>\n<p>小酌或者应酬后想了解自己的身体状况？来自美国的 Edge Tech Labs 希望通过这款世界上最小的酒精测量仪 DrinkMate 让这个过程变得方便又卫生。它的进气口经过特殊设计，可以将呼出的气体精准地引导至内置的感应器中，免去了口腔的直接接触。使用时只需要把它插入手机（这也是它的电力来源），对着它轻轻吹一口气，配套的软件就会显示出血液酒精浓度（BAC）。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/drinkmate-the-miniature-smartphone-breathalyzer#/\">链接</a>购买这个小巧的测醉器，售价为 35 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021602250C1BAUa3Z6JoghYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59347181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160225iIjakZywxeurzYWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160226Xp3N1SYZ54hf9uzK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160226DBHNZ5rcCiAGRSTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62580645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160228NgJOba4KHITeZsrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160228n19RlzgMu8soi6WB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>El Golfo de México by Colateral Advanced Marketing</h2>\n<p>看腻了大红大金的烈酒包装？<a href=\"http://colateralmkt.com/\">Colateral Advanced Marketing</a> 的设计师们带来了一个另辟蹊径的创意：通过海洋元素来表现一款墨西哥的梅斯卡尔酒（mezcal，是龙舌兰酒的一种）El Golfo de México。印有小船锚的木塞封住了纤细透明的瓶身，采用蓝黑配色在包装上印上了海底以及抽着烟斗的大胡子水手的图像，带给人一种清新明亮的感觉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160229cxBmZ1aDMA43GCTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160230QZi0DdJoXpqnRv5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160230Vh9StN4olcpAr6TY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160231UfHqsAv1npdLQDFw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}